<section class="section section-centered" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">

        <h2 class="section-header">About Juxta</h2>

        <p>
          Welcome to Juxta Productions, a performing arts company that offers
          holiday workshops to young people. We give them the opportunity to develop their
          skills as talented performers as well as their confidence, creativity
          and interpersonal skills.
        </p>

        <p>
          Juxta Productions enjoy working with young people on both scripted
          and improvised performances and each workshop is tailored to the strengths
          and interests of the group. All week long workshops finish with a
          final showcase in which the young people will perform to an invited audience.
        </p>

        <div>
          <br>
          <%= partial "partials/social-btns" %>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-centered" id="team">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-1">

        <h2 class="section-header">Meet the team</h2>

        <p>
          Eve and David have been working together in and out of education for the past
          ten years. With years of experience behind them in both teaching (including
          qualified teacher status) and performing; you will not be disappointed by
          the professional service you will receive.
        </p>

        <p>
          As well as teaching between them Performing Arts, Drama and Dance; both
          have directed and choreographed in productions such as We Will Rock You,
          Grease, Bugsy Malone, Oliver, The 39 Steps and Alice in Wonderland to name a few.
          They have had the privilege of performing over the years in theatre,
          pantomimes and dance shows at prestigious venues across the country.
        </p>

        <p>
          With a passion for Theatre and the Arts, Eve and David know how to interest
          and challenge young people and are excited about being able to offer something
          new and exciting.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <div class="avatars avatars-align-right">
          <div class="avatar avatar-round avatar-list">
            <img src="images/avatar-david.jpg" width="200" height="200" alt="David Routledge">
            <h4>David Routledge</h4>
          </div>

          <div class="avatar avatar-round avatar-list">
            <img src="images/avatar-eve.jpg" width="200" height="200" alt="Eve Santamaria">
            <h4>Eve Santamaria</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

